column1: Nielíqui was a Valar maiden only appearing in the earliest version of the legendarium. She was the daughter of Oromë and Vána.
column3: p. 288 She also enjoyed dancing through her fathers Woods of Oromë and Ómar would sometimes accompany her by singing along.

column1: Nielikki was perhaps intended to be a "pet-name form" of Nieliqi.
Category:Characters in The Book of Lost Tales
